               <msContents>
                  <summary>
                     <p>I) መጽሐፈ፡ግጻዌ, Lectionary for the days of the week (fols. <locus from="3r" to="41v"/>)  </p>
                     <p>I-<locus target="#1"/>) ባርከነ፡እግዚኦ፡... “Bless us, o Lord…”, prayer of blessing (fols. <locus from="3ra" to="5vb"/>) </p>
                     <p>I-<locus target="#2"/>) Biblical readings (fols. <locus from="6ra" to="41vb"/>)</p>
                     
                     
                     
                  </summary>

               </msContents>
